  = link_to "Donate", "https://www.openaustraliafoundation.org.au/donate/planningalerts/", :class => "button button-rounded button-action button-large"

%p.attention
  %small
    We are
    = link_to "a Charitable Institution with Deductible Gift Recipient (DGR) status", "http://abr.business.gov.au/SearchByAbn.aspx?abn=24138089942"
